Installation

git clone git@github.com:darrent/winvim.git

del _vimrc

mklink _vimrc winvim\_vimrc
mklink _gvimrc winvim\_gvimrc
mklink /D vimfiles winvim

cd winvim

git submodule init
git submodule update

Adding submodules

git submodule add [gitpath] bundle/[plugin-name]

Updating submodules

cd bundle/[plugin-name]
git pull origin master


Updateing all submodule

git submodule foreach git pull origin master